name: fasting
title: willingly abstaining for a period of time
description: The great comedian, Ed Wynn said, "Without your health, riches, possessions and fame are all mud." With the high costs of health care, how can we *afford* not to keep ourselves well? Perhaps no subject is less understood by the public and the "healing" professions than this oldest of means of caring for the sick body.
